'''2010年冬季奥林匹克运动会埃塞俄比亚代表团'''于2010年2月参加了在[[加拿大|加拿大]][[温哥华|温哥华]]举行的[[2010年冬季奥林匹克运动会|第21届冬奥会]]。这是埃塞俄比亚第二次参加冬奥会，与[[2006年冬季奥林匹克运动会埃塞俄比亚代表团|四年前]]一样，埃塞俄比亚只派出了越野滑雪运动员{{tsl|en|Robel Teklemariam|罗贝尔·雷马里安|}}参赛。雷马里安最终在15千米自由式越野滑雪比赛中取得第93名。
[[File:2010_Opening_Ceremony_-_Ethiopia_entering.jpg|右]]

== 背景 ==
埃塞俄比亚第一次参加[[夏季奥运会|夏季奥运会]]是在1956年的澳大利亚[[1956年夏季奥林匹克运动会|墨尔本奥运会]]上。除[[1976年夏季奥林匹克运动会|1976年]]、[[1984年夏季奥林匹克运动会|1984年]]和[[1988年夏季奥林匹克运动会|1988年]]外，埃塞俄比亚参加了此后的每届夏季奥运会。2006年的意大利[[2006年冬季奥林匹克运动会|都灵冬奥会]]是埃塞俄比亚第一次参加冬季奥运会<ref>{{cite web|title=Ethiopia|url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/countries/ETH/|publisher=Sports Reference|access-date=2018-05-05|dead-url=yes|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200417093603/https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/countries/ETH/|archive-date=2020-04-17}}</ref>，埃塞俄比亚仅派出{{tsl|en|Robel Teklemariam|罗贝尔·雷马里安|}}一人，参加越野滑雪比赛，最终取得第83名<ref name="NYT">{{cite news|url=https://vancouver2010.blogs.nytimes.com/2010/02/12/ones-to-know-robel-teklemariam/|title=Ones to Know: Robel Teklemariam|last=Crouse|first=Karen|date=2010-02-12|work=[[纽约时报|The New York Times]]|accessdate=2018-05-11|archive-date=2020-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201009073247/https://vancouver2010.blogs.nytimes.com/2010/02/12/ones-to-know-robel-teklemariam/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。与四年前一样，埃塞俄比亚仅派出雷马里安参加该届冬奥会<ref>{{cite web|title=Ethiopia at the 2006 Torino Winter Games|url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/countries/ETH/winter/2006/|publisher=Sports Reference|access-date=2018-05-05|dead-url=yes|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170712193422/http://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/countries/ETH/winter/2006/|archive-date=2017-07-12}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Ethiopia at the 2010 Vancouver Winter Games|url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/countries/ETH/winter/2010/|publisher=Sports Reference|access-date=2018-05-05|dead-url=yes|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170712193523/http://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/countries/ETH/winter/2010/|archive-date=2017-07-12}}</ref>。他出生于埃塞俄比亚，在美国[[纽约|纽约]][[普莱西德湖|普莱西德湖]]生活时开始学习滑雪，之后回到埃塞俄比亚并参与建立埃塞俄比亚滑雪协会<ref>{{cite web|title=Olympic Skier From, Uh ... Ethiopia|url=https://abcnews.go.com/International/ethiopian-skier-competes-winter-olympics/story?id=9821138|date=2010-02-13|last=Hughes|first=Dana|publisher=ABC News|access-date=2018-05-05|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170803130255/http://abcnews.go.com/International/ethiopian-skier-competes-winter-olympics/story?id=9821138|archive-date=2017-08-03}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Jamaican Bobsleigh? No, Ethiopian ski team!|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-olympics-alpineskiing-ethiopia-idUSBREA1E06T20140215|date=2014-02-15|last=Young|first=Ben|publisher=[[路透社|Reuters]]|access-date=2018-05-05|dead-url=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161107155045/http://www.reuters.com/article/us-olympics-alpineskiing-ethiopia-idUSBREA1E06T20140215|archive-date=2016-11-07}}</ref>。雷马里安还被选为[[2010年冬季奧林匹克運動會開幕式|开幕式]]与{{tsl|en|2010 Winter Olympics closing ceremony|2010年冬季奥林匹克运动会闭幕式|闭幕式}}上的旗手<ref>{{cite news|url=https://vancouversun.com/sports/Complete+list+2010+Vancouver+Winter+Olympic+flag+bearers/2558064/story.html|title=Complete list of 2010 Vancouver Winter Olympic flag-bearers|date=2010-02-12|work=[[溫哥華太陽報|The Vancouver Sun]]|accessdate=2018-04-29|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100216123527/http://www.vancouversun.com/sports/Complete%2Blist%2B2010%2BVancouver%2BWinter%2BOlympic%2Bflag%2Bbearers/2558064/story.html|archivedate=2010-02-16|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=The Flagbearers for the Vancouver 2010 Closing Ceremony|url=http://www.olympic.org/Documents/Games_Vancouver_2010/ClosingCeremonyFlagbearers-eng.pdf|date=2010-02-28|publisher=[[国际奥林匹克委员会|International Olympic Committee]]|access-date=2018-04-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100401032223/http://www.olympic.org/Documents/Games_Vancouver_2010/ClosingCeremonyFlagbearers-eng.pdf|archive-date=2010-04-01|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

==  [[File:Cross_country_skiing_pictogram.svg|30px]] 越野滑雪==
{{main|2010年冬季奥林匹克运动会越野滑雪比赛}}
参加温哥华冬奥会时，{{tsl|en|Robel Teklemariam|罗贝尔·雷马里安|}}已经35岁<ref>{{cite web|title=Robel Teklemariam Bio, Stats, and Results|url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/te/robel-teklemariam-1.html|publisher=Sports Reference|access-date=2018-05-05|dead-url=yes|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170803135536/https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/te/robel-teklemariam-1.html|archive-date=2017-08-03}}</ref>。他以在[[亚的斯亚贝巴|亚的斯亚贝巴]]街头滑[[旱冰|旱冰]]的方式进行训练<ref>{{cite web|title=Robel Teklemariam is the Ethiopian Olympic team|url=https://sports.yahoo.com/blogs/olympics-fourth-place-medal/robel-teklemariam-ethiopian-olympic-team--olympics.html|accessdate=2018-05-11|date=2010-02-12|last=Kerby|first=Trey|publisher=[[雅虎|Yahoo!]]|archive-date=2018-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180511215531/https://sports.yahoo.com/blogs/olympics-fourth-place-medal/robel-teklemariam-ethiopian-olympic-team--olympics.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他说他在温哥华冬奥会上的目标是“在意大利冬奥会的基础上更进一步，激励埃塞俄比亚的年轻人追随他的足迹”<ref name="NYT" />。2010年2月15日，他参加了{{tsl|en|Cross-country skiing at the 2010 Winter Olympics – Men's 15 kilometre freestyle|2010年冬季奥林匹克运动会越野滑雪比赛 – 男子15公里自由式|男子15公里自由式}}越野滑雪比赛，以45分18秒的成绩完赛，与金牌得主的成绩相差近12分钟<ref>{{cite web|title=Cross Country Skiing at the 2010 Vancouver Winter Games: Men's 15 kilometres|url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/winter/2010/CCS/mens-15-kilometres.html|publisher=Sports Reference|access-date=2018-05-05|dead-url=yes|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150921165136/http://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/winter/2010/CCS/mens-15-kilometres.html|archive-date=2015-09-21}}</ref>。在完成比赛的95名选手中，他排在第93位<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.richmond.com/news/robel-teklemariam-places-rd-in-cross-country-ski-event/article_ba432391-357b-5a73-ab78-1dff725fc60c.html|title=Robel Teklemariam places 93rd in cross country ski event|last=Phillips|first=Michael|date=2010-02-16|work={{tsl|en|Richmond Times-Dispatch||Richmond Times-Dispatch}}|accessdate=2018-05-05}}</ref>。
